reviewText: Bad quality, not worth the money.
A fanciful, artistic interpretation of fairy tales that is like a dream you don't want to end.

Awesome, beautiful silhouette animated fairy tales.  This is a must-have if you're a Lotte Reiniger fan, a silhouette animation fan, or a fan of early animation.  The cover states the DVD is silent, but there is sound on many of the film shorts.  SO highly recommended!
